{
  "stem": "1160.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But a good building, not just any kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's a nice one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I'm-- I didn't listen again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I didn't stay with grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My other siblings did, but I-- I had to see what's going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then I'm very anxious, because everybody's scared.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were saying, hurry up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Hurry up before they come-- before the German comes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Hurry up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Hurry up.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because they left-- sort of they left us there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And-- and I was worried that my mother should already be able to do something, what she wanted, with this cooking.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then suddenly, somebody says, look, they're coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I'm-- my heart in my throat and I start to tell my mother, come on out, come on out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It wasn't so easy to come out from this trench, because it was deep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Somebody had to, you know, put a hand down and help you out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And most of the people got out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But three of them-- I think three of them, but maybe there was more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But three, somehow, I remember, they just couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The rest of them were already too scared to stay there and help.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Everybody was just running back to their little bundles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And again, I saw something fascinating.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And with my child's mind, I-- something-- I always find something fascinating to watch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I turn around, at the trench, and I couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why couldn't I move?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I said in my mind, how on earth can you run so fast?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I see this time not just men.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I see women also-- and we were told they were Ukrainians-- stick in their hands-- rubber stick in their hands-- and they are running so fast.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But how fast they are running?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
